        <p>Procedimentos estéticos para realçar a beleza natural do seu rosto de forma harmoniosa e segura.</p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Toxina botulínica</li>
          <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Preenchimento facial</li>
          <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Fios de sustentação</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-card fade-in">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <i data-lucide="activity"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Endodontia</h3>
        <p>Tratamento de canal moderno e indolor, preservando seus dentes naturais com máximo conforto.</p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Tratamento indolor</li>
          <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Tecnologia digital</li>
          <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Preservação dental</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="services-cta fade-in">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h3>Não encontrou o que procura?</h3>
        <p>Entre em contato conosco para uma avaliação personalizada</p>
        <a href="#contato" class="btn btn-primary">
          <i data-lucide="phone"></i>
          Falar com Especialista
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.services {
  background: var(--bg-secondary);
}

.section-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 4rem;
}

.section-header h2 {
  color: var(--text-primary);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.section-header p {
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.services-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
  gap: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 4rem;
}

.service-card {
  background: white;
  border-radius: 1rem;
  padding: 2rem;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-medium);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.service-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 4px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
  transform: translateX(-100%);
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.service-card:hover::before {
  transform: translateX(0);
}

.service-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-8px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-large);
}

.service-icon {
  width: 4rem;
  height: 4rem;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--primary-light));
  border-radius: 1rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  color: white;
}

.service-icon i {
  width: 2rem;
  height: 2rem;
}

.service-card h3 {
  color: var(--text-primary);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
}

.service-card p {
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.service-features {
  list-style: none;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

.service-features li {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  font-size: 0.875rem;
}

.service-features li:last-child {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

.service-features i {
  width: 1rem;
  height: 1rem;
  color: var(--secondary-color);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.services-cta {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--primary-light));
  border-radius: 1.5rem;
  padding: 3rem 2rem;
  text-align: center;
  color: white;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.services-cta::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: -50%;
  right: -50%;
  width: 100%;
  height: 200%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.cta-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.services-cta h3 {
  color: white;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  font-size: 1.75rem;
}

.services-cta p {
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  font-size: 1.125rem;
}

.services-cta .btn {
  background: white;
  color: var(--primary-color);
}

.services-cta .btn:hover {
  background: var(--bg-secondary);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .services-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .service-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .services-cta {
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .services-cta h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .service-card {
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }
  
  .service-icon {
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
  }
  
  .service-icon i {
    width: 1.5rem;
    height: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .service-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }
}
</style>

<script>
// Initialize Lucide icons
lucide.createIcons();

// Fade in animation on scroll (reuse from previous components)
const observerOptions = {
  threshold: 0.1,
  rootMargin: '0px 0px -50px 0px'
};

const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
  entries.forEach(entry => {
    if (entry.isIntersecting) {
      entry.target.classList.add('visible');
    }
  });
}, observerOptions);

// Observe all fade-in elements in this section
document.querySelectorAll('.services .fade-in').forEach(el => {
  observer.observe(el);
});
</script>
